snippet.title: Nekoparaiten! Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Nekoparaiten is an anime Neko romance simulation mobile game. Welcome to a new cats paradise where all kinds of nekos over the world will gather around you.

Creator: Sayori (NEKO WORKs)

Developed by Yostar Games

#Nekoparaiten #AX2019
